Happy Saturday everyone!! 🙋🏻‍♂️🌻🐝🐒😄
2 more days to Phase 1 of post-circuit breaker period. Rewarding myself for being a responsible citizen with old school ice cream from Uncle Lim. Sure brings back fond childhood memories.

Check out their IG account for ordering details.
.
Thanks @unclelimoldschoolicecream_ for sending over these frozen treats 🍦😋
